无限滚动的栗子:

```js
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>intersectionObserve</title>
		<style type="text/css">
			.img {
				height: 1200px;
				overflow: hidden;
			}
			#flag {
